✨ The Luxe Code at Lumara ✨

A curated celebration of fashion, style, and statement pieces. Join us for a designer showcase like no other, featuring 20+ iconic labels — from bold couture to effortless elegance. 🌿👗

@tasnneem_ at Lumara this Friday🚨 

RSVP in the link @eclipsefridays ➡️

This Friday at Eclipse 🌙

A night of deeper grooves, layered rhythms, and rooftop energy incoming —

We’ve got @tasnneem_ taking control of the decks — an excellent DJ & producer with a taste for immersive sounds and powerful builds. She’ll be bringing the heat to the Lumara rooftop for her Eclipse debut.

@skychan.music returns on opening duties — setting the tone with his signature warm-up style and slow-burning energy.

Come early, stay late — let the music do the rest.

📅 Friday, June 20
📍 Lumara Bar & Kitchen – 9PM onwards
🎟️ Limited Entry by RSVP only
